text: Clubul Sportiv Orășenesc Voluntari, commonly known as CSO Voluntari or simply Voluntari, is a Romanian basketball club based in Voluntari, currently participates in the Liga Națională, the top-tier league in Romania. The club initially played in the second-tier Liga I. However, in 2018 the league was merged with the top-tier Liga Națională.Cum va arăta Liga Națională de Baschet Masculin sezonul viitor. totalbaschet.ro ==Current roster== ==References== ==External links== Category:2005 establishments in Romania Category:Basketball teams in Romania Category:Basketball teams established in 2005
